# Admin Portal Design System

**Status**: Baseline established from PROJ-325 Figma designs
**Last Updated**: 2026-01-13
**Figma Reference**: [Admin Portal Designs](https://www.figma.com/design/YOUR_FILE_ID/Your-Design-File?node-id=YOUR_NODE_ID)

---

## 1. Design Philosophy

The Admin Portal design system is **distinct from the public-facing web-app design system**. It is optimized for:

- **Internal tooling**: Government administrators and data curators
- **Data density**: Tables, lists, and information-rich interfaces
- **Desktop-first**: Not designed for mobile/responsive (per requirements)
- **Efficiency**: Rapid task completion over marketing aesthetics

**Key Difference**: Admin uses smaller typography, tighter spacing, and sidebar-based navigation vs. web's header-based navigation.

---

## 2. Typography System

### 2.1 Font Configuration

**Primary Font**: Roboto via `next/font/google`

**Weights Required**:

- 400 (Regular)
- 500 (Medium) - **NEW for admin**
- 600 (SemiBold) - **NEW for admin**
- 700 (Bold)
- 800 (ExtraBold) - if needed for future headers

**Configuration** (`app/layout.tsx`):

```tsx
import { Roboto } from 'next/font/google'

const roboto = Roboto({
  weight: ['400', '500', '600', '700', '800'],
  subsets: ['latin'],
  variable: '--font-roboto',
  display: 'swap',
})
```

### 2.2 Typography Scale (Admin-Specific)

| Element                    | Size | Line Height | Weight         | Usage                       | Token              |
| -------------------------- | ---- | ----------- | -------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------ |
| **Page Title**             | 30px | 36px        | 700 (Bold)     | H1 page headings            | `heading-md`       |
| **Section Heading**        | 20px | Normal      | 700 (Bold)     | Section headers (if needed) | Custom             |
| **Sidebar Menu (Active)**  | 14px | 20px        | 500 (Medium)   | Active navigation item      | `text-sm/medium`   |
| **Sidebar Menu (Default)** | 14px | 20px        | 400 (Regular)  | Default navigation item     | `text-sm/normal`   |
| **Sidebar Header**         | 14px | None (1)    | 600 (SemiBold) | "[Name] Admin Portal"       | `text-sm/semibold` |
| **Sidebar Subtext**        | 12px | None (1)    | 400 (Regular)  | "Super Admin View", email   | `text-xs/normal`   |
| **Table Header**           | 14px | 20px        | 500 (Medium)   | Column headers              | `text-sm/medium`   |
| **Table Body**             | 14px | 20px        | 400 (Regular)  | Table cell content          | `text-sm/normal`   |
| **Button Text**            | 14px | 20px        | 500 (Medium)   | All button labels           | `text-sm/medium`   |
| **Input Text**             | 14px | 20px        | 400 (Regular)  | Form inputs, placeholders   | `text-sm/normal`   |

### 2.3 Typography Implementation

**Design Token Variables** (from Figma):

```css
