**Tailwind Classes**:

```tsx
// Page title (H1)
<h1 className="text-[30px] leading-[36px] font-bold">Targeted Resources</h1>

// Sidebar menu item (active)
<p className="text-sm leading-5 font-medium">Dashboard</p>

// Sidebar menu item (default)
