### 2.4 Semantic HTML with Admin Styling

**Page Titles**: Use `<h1>` for accessibility, styled to 30px:

```tsx
// ✅ Correct - semantic HTML with custom admin styling
<h1 className="text-[30px] leading-[36px] font-bold text-foreground">{pageTitle}</h1>
```

**Rationale**: Admin page titles are semantic headings but styled for dense UI, not marketing scale.

