## 3. Color System

### 3.1 OKLCH Color Palette

**Admin-Specific Colors** (converted from Figma hex):

```css
/* Sidebar colors */
--sidebar-background: oklch(0.98 0 0); /* #fafafa */
--sidebar-foreground: oklch(0.15 0 0); /* #0a0a0a */
--sidebar-primary: oklch(0.2 0 0); /* #171717 */
--sidebar-accent: oklch(0.96 0 0); /* #f5f5f5 - active state */
--sidebar-accent-foreground: oklch(0.2 0 0); /* #171717 */

/* Shared with web-app */
