### 3.2 Color Usage Patterns

| Element                 | Color Token          | Hex     | Usage                        |
| ----------------------- | -------------------- | ------- | ---------------------------- |
| Sidebar background      | `sidebar-background` | #fafafa | Fixed sidebar                |
| Sidebar text (default)  | `sidebar-foreground` | #0a0a0a | Menu items, user info        |
| Sidebar icon background | `sidebar-primary`    | #171717 | Avatar/icon containers       |
| Sidebar active state    | `sidebar-accent`     | #f5f5f5 | Active menu item background  |
| Page background         | `background`         | #ffffff | Main content area            |
| Page text               | `foreground`         | #0f172a | Headers, body text           |
| Table headers           | `muted-foreground`   | #737373 | Column headers               |
| Borders                 | `border`             | #e5e5e5 | Table borders, input borders |
| Secondary buttons       | `secondary`          | #f5f5f5 | "Add Resource" button        |

