## 10. Differences from web-app Design System

| Aspect            | web-app (Public)            | admin-app (Internal)        |
| ----------------- | --------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| **Typography**    | 48px H1, 16px body          | 30px page title, 14px body  |
| **Navigation**    | Header-based                | Sidebar-based               |
| **Layout**        | Content-first, spacious     | Data-dense, efficient       |
| **Responsive**    | Mobile-first (360px+)       | Desktop-only (1440px+)      |
| **Color Palette** | Marketing-focused           | Neutral grays, data-focused |
| **Spacing**       | Generous (24px, 32px gaps)  | Compact (8px, 4px gaps)     |
| **Font Weights**  | 400, 700, 800               | 400, 500, 600, 700          |
| **Components**    | Hero, cards, marketing CTAs | Tables, forms, data views   |

