## 12. Implementation Checklist

When implementing admin portal features:

- [ ] Use 14px (text-sm) as default text size, not 16px
- [ ] Page titles are 30px (heading-md), not 48px
- [ ] Use sidebar color tokens for navigation
- [ ] Tables use 40px header height, 57px row height
- [ ] All icons are 16x16px (size-4)
- [ ] No mobile/responsive breakpoints (desktop-only)
- [ ] Semantic HTML (`<h1>`, `<nav>`, `<table>`) with admin styling
- [ ] ChevronRight icons are decorative (`aria-hidden="true"`)
- [ ] Font weights: 500 (Medium) and 600 (SemiBold) are available
- [ ] Verify all design tokens are defined in `app/globals.css`

